\v 8  \w Rehum|strong="H7348"\w* \w the|strong="H5922"\w* \w commander|strong="H1169"\w* \w and|strong="H4430"\w* \w Shimshai|strong="H8124"\w* \w the|strong="H5922"\w* \w scribe|strong="H5613"\w* \w wrote|strong="H3790"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* letter \w concerning|strong="H5922"\w* \w Jerusalem|strong="H3390"\w* \w to|strong="H5922"\w* \w King|strong="H4430"\w* Artaxerxes as \w follows|strong="H3660"\w*:  
